    "title": "Career Opportunity Medical Officer at Columbia Asia Advisory Limited",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Medical Officer with drive and ambition, Columbia Asia Advisory Limited in Jaipur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Columbia Asia Advisory Limited:\nColumbia Asia Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Columbia Asia Advisory Limited!",
